  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要一个任务状态流转图，从待办开始，经过进行中、评审，最后到完成。另外还要考虑任务被取消的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "todo",
        "doing",
        "review",
        "done",
        "archived/cancelled"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。起点用[*]表示，然后先到todo状态对吗？另外，从todo可以直接取消吗，还是必须先开始才能取消？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "todo",
        "archived/cancelled"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，起点到todo。另外todo可以直接归档或取消，不需要先开始。这个路径很重要，很多任务还没开始就取消了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "todo",
        "archived/cancelled"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我画一下：起点连到todo，todo可以start到doing，doing完成实现后进入review。评审通过就到done，不通过的话打回doing修改。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "todo",
        "doing",
        "review",
        "done",
        "start",
        "implementation complete",
        "validated",
        "changes requested"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，doing到review的触发条件我写的是\"implementation complete\"，你刚才说的是\"完成实现\"，确认一下标签要英文还是中文？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "doing",
        "review",
        "implementation complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "用英文标签\"implementation complete\"保持一致性。那review到done是\"validated\"，review回退到doing是\"changes requested\"，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "review",
        "done",
        "doing",
        "validated",
        "changes requested"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对的。最后done和那个取消的路径都要能到终点[*]，表示流程结束。用stateDiagram-v2来画。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "done",
        "archived/cancelled",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。整个流转：起点→todo→doing→review→done→终点，todo也可以直接取消到终点，review不通过能回doing，所有终态都连到[*]。",
